拜访他的祖父母。门票价格为 30 英镑—— <a href="https://www.skiddle.com/whats-on/Liverpool/The-Cavern-Club/Mantra-of-the-Cosmos/40406756/?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAabWhDkucc4MoM-3MJKHX33H1Jb4ZDoU-_9EN1P-lL1b-r9gjxXSSb6Hm1s_aem_Wyh77bLW7Bb8lWMCtRqJdQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买</a>。</p><p> Starkey 于 2004 年开始为 Oasis 打鼓，并在他们的最后两张专辑“Don&#39;t Believe The Truth”（2005 年）和“Dig Your Own Soul”（2008 年）中演奏。目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">有传言称，他将与前成员安迪·贝尔 (Andy Bell) 一起加入新的绿洲乐队</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-more-dates-added-to-2025-tour-due-to-unprecedented-demand-3788543">2025 年大型重聚巡演</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3452319" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3452319" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3452319" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo.jpg" alt="宇宙咒语，摄影：Andrzej Liguz/Neil Cooper" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3452319" class="wp-caption-text">宇宙咒。图片来源：Andrzej Liguz/尼尔·库珀</figcaption></figure><p>“我第一次见到诺埃尔是在伦敦啤酒厂路约翰·亨利的排练室，”斯塔基回忆道。 “在英伦流行音乐时代，我加入了一支名为 Face 的乐队，那是 1995 年初，他进来看了一会儿。我第一次见到他的兄弟是在 1996 年 Oasis 的 Earls Court 演出上。我们是 Mods，所以我们很快就相处得很融洽。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="http